{% comment %}
	theme js is deferred, so we have to defer these files as well
	the files are located in /local/pages/* and copied into the assets folder via gulp's pages task
	this is by no means a best-practice, but we needed a way to copy over individual page customizations inlined by WP
{% endcomment %}

